blog.name: weirdandwackypokefusions
blog.title: Well that's strange!
blog.description:
Welcome!  I create, using the all-mighty classic Microsoft XP Paint, my own pokemon fusions. All the sprites come from pokestadium and usually people on deviantart/ the xy/sun&moon sprite project. I don't own any of the sprite used, I just fuse them! 
REQUESTS ARE OPEN! Ask Box: 3/15.
PLEASE FEEL FREE TO DRAW MY FUSIONS!!  I absolutely love it when people draw them! There's no need to ask either! Just make sure you tag me so them I can see it!
I hope you enjoy my fusions!

summary: Flarachu Flareon and Pikachu fusion Electric/Fire type Ability: Static Hidden Ability: Flame Body The Shocking Rodent Pokemon...
caption:
Flarachu

Flareon and Pikachu fusion

Electric/Fire type

Ability: Static

Hidden Ability: Flame Body

The Shocking Rodent Pokemon

This pokefusion’s fluff sends static shocks to people who touch it.  It’s a very confident pokefusion and always wants to prove itself to its trainer. 

Request for @frisk-the-flareon.  I hope you like it! And it’s not that your first request wasn’t good.  It’s my fault for not making a rules list! I really need to do that.
